{
  "stem": "22734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "You never convinced her otherwise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "You know, it was a set of circumstances.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And you never, never convinced her otherwise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But she-- she lost her sense of humor or judgment after she was in jail.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "After she came back, she-- she-- she never became-- she never was herself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And then, they let me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And then, it was-- I worked with-- with newborn children in Terezin, newborn babies because some girls came pregnant from other parts of the world, from Prague.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And-- and they were-- and they gave birth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And these children, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was sad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They were like little rabbits.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They-- the girls had no milk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And-- and we boiled everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And we tried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Anyway, nobody survived, neither the mothers nor the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And then, at Christmastime, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Ruda's ?] parents came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And my father came straight from jail in his jail clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And the funny part of it is that my in-laws, they-- for them I was the long lost daughter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And it was all fine, even though I was-- I wasn't 16 yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "You know, my mother was desperate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I can-- I think, if [? my Mischa ?] would do this to me, I would be desperate too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "I can sympathize with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "But those were desperate times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father just also thought it was absolutely, positively wonderful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why not?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- he-- he was very-- he was very upbeat about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for my mother-in-law, I was the daughter she lost.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even after the war, she was-- she would be mad at [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ruda, ?] but I could do no wrong, whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Evicka-- you asked me what they called me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't call me Eva.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called me Evicka.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Evicka was a saint.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, that-- you call people [INAUDIBLE] the diminutive.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
